Server Side Requirements
-----------------------------
1. Apache, IIS or NGINX web server
  The rewrite code (.htaccess) is only tested under apache.

2. php 5.3 or newer
  "short_open_tag" should be set to "On" in php 5.3 ini, while unnecessarily in php 5.4 and newer.

3. MySQL 5
  Tested under MySQL 5.6, but no edge techs is applied, which means MySQL 5.0 and newer version should also works.

Client Side Requirements
------------------------------
All visual elements are tested under IE9 and newer, Chrome, Safari and Firefox.
Some visual effects lost under IE8, such as box shadows and border radius.